Summary: i saw about 10 red lights in line formation coming over the mountains.
divs: Sighting Detailsit was about 730pm we were waiting in the parking lot. I looked over at these red lights coming over the mountains in line formation.i thought maybe military parachuting, but once the red lights got over the mountains it looked like they all spread out then lifted up higher into the sky all together all at the same time and pace then disappeared.
